Class Rectangle

java.lang.Object
  Rectangle
Direct Known Subclasses:
MobileObject, Wall
public abstract class Rectangle
extends java.lang.Object

This class has abstract methods for the Wall and MobileObject Classes. It provides simple access to the single coordinate values to the sides of the rectangle. It also requires all Rectangles with test methods for simulating movement and determining the maximum distance able to move according to the distance passed as a parameter.
